own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012938a394d763fa586bb638651831ae3675cba7","tid":367813,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"試過完全唔想問舊同事<br />\n因為一句偈都無傾過<br />\n但經理係咁逼鳩我打電話問舊同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b86338a0d9b6d38e7bf972720df034e693cd5c8","tid":367813,"uid":1993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:45:15.000Z","msg":"Friend底先答"},{"pid":"e9603c0b8105b280030941394879b44120641327","tid":367813,"uid":37487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無做好handover? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔比樓豬起飛腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a66f3444d8f6f47081944f3fa6a7135261900f4","tid":367813,"uid":72979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:15:52.000Z","msg":"我想問下<br />\n調番轉呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係走左舊公司年幾左右<br />\n想打番去公司問野/拎番証明之類<br />\n會唔會好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:舊公司係我自己走 大家都叫好黎好去"},{"pid":"595c4c5c8bfcfe63de3277abe48488652a2ae455","tid":367813,"uid":125087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:23:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>轉左工一個月左右，接左不下十個佢地電話，舊老細舊teammate, 打來問以前我跟既case<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我點撚記得</blockquote><br />\n打錯電話！<br />\n利申：fd底嘅會答，其他果啲你諗你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係睇交情 畀我最多答三次 仁至義盡"},{"pid":"e03b441f5d0c74d70daf73723fac50d63e2ece57","tid":367813,"uid":77731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"過多個零月唔需要再答"}]}